translated: Luckey, Ewald, director, Lysekil, b. 10/5/98 in Lysekil to factory owner Elis L. and Amanda Christensson. Married on 28 with Märta Olsson. Children: Lars b. 29, Lena b. 31, Kaj b. 36. - Graduated from Realex., Gbgs Handelsinstitut. Dispersed and served as executive director at A-B Elis Luckey's canned food factory. Member of the city council since 1932, member of the civilian defense, vice-chairman of the financial committee and the Swedish Canned Food Manufacturers Association. Chairman of the trade and maritime board, head and member of the board in Sparbanken, vice-chairman of Lysekil's conservative association, board member of the Swedish herring and fish importers association in Stockholm, member of the 47-year fish industry investigation. Traveled to England and Germany.
